external_knowledge:
'Closed properties' refers to properties with a status of 'CLS'.;
The 'agents' are the personnel responsible for listing the properties.;
Office names uniquely identify each office in the database.;

sql:
SELECT agents.agent_name, properties.city
FROM properties
JOIN agents ON properties.agent_id = agents.agent_id;

SELECT AVG(commission) AS average_commission
FROM transactions
WHERE status = 'completed';

external_knowledge:
The term "top performers" refers to the agents with the highest total sales amounts; the ranking is determined based on this metric. The rank of 1 indicates the highest performing agent.;
The total sales amount is the cumulative value of all transactions made by each agent.;
Transaction count refers to the total number of transactions each agent has facilitated.;

sql:
SELECT a.agent_name, a.email, a.phone, o.office_name
FROM agents a
INNER JOIN offices o ON a.office_id = o.office_id;
